    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wordlike is a word roguelike—make words, tune your bag of letters, and collect power-ups to beat increasingly difficult levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you've played Balatro, it's like Balatro with words 🔠</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A word-based deckbuilder </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat each round by constructing words, and tune your bag of letters to optimize your draws.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/c42de5b3dca38bf3a70234a1603e3fe4.poster.avif?t=1744381940\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/c42de5b3dca38bf3a70234a1603e3fe4.webm?t=1744381940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/c42de5b3dca38bf3a70234a1603e3fe4.mp4?t=1744381940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Powerful 'Knick Knacks' </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy Knick Knacks to boost your score, enhance letters, and tune your bag. Discover unique word-based synergies based on parts of speech, letters, slang, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/d4c831f6bbfc2ef62c06e979b85405e4.poster.avif?t=1744381940\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/d4c831f6bbfc2ef62c06e979b85405e4.webm?t=1744381940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/d4c831f6bbfc2ef62c06e979b85405e4.mp4?t=1744381940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Face challenging bosses </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter a variety of bosses that challenge you to make words without consonants, avoid nouns, or make words you've never made before.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/b5ac8bd5d14866c6f5c511ce0084985b.poster.avif?t=1744381940\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/b5ac8bd5d14866c6f5c511ce0084985b.webm?t=1744381940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/b5ac8bd5d14866c6f5c511ce0084985b.mp4?t=1744381940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique runs every time</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each play through brings you a different bag of letters, unique bosses, and different sets of items that you can put together to make a strong build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/23f8527a2422dac54e160fdf0531a802.poster.avif?t=1744381940\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/23f8527a2422dac54e160fdf0531a802.webm?t=1744381940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/23f8527a2422dac54e160fdf0531a802.mp4?t=1744381940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Variety of tile enhancements</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create unique builds by employing a variety of different tiles and special abilities - leather, velvet, diamond, and more tiles await.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/911850e53a134e0d7d99704076d08ace.poster.avif?t=1744381940\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/911850e53a134e0d7d99704076d08ace.webm?t=1744381940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/911850e53a134e0d7d99704076d08ace.mp4?t=1744381940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
